==English==

===Adverb===
'''variably'''

# In a [[variable]] manner.
#:''Such facts as the complex and extraordinary out growths which '''variably''' follow from the insertion of a minute drop of poison by a gall-producing insect, shows us what singular modifications might result in the case of plants from a chemical change in the nature of the sap.'' — Charles Darwin, ''The Origin of Species'', [[s:The Origin of Species, Chapter 1 - Variation Under Domestication|Chapter 1]].